{"tid":145680,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"[突發]疑似班耶撚搞到我facebook page 都用唔到","createTime":"2017-03-06T12:24:49.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-13T20:02:52.000Z","uid":80991,"like":89,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"99c8e5d267ef52164389931b979f9da84fedcd7b","tid":145680,"uid":80991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T12:24:49.000Z","msg":"各位大家好又係我, 思古井。<br />\n首先好多謝大家對我連日嘅關心。<br />\n<br />\n相信大家都知道我發生緊咩事,<br />\n我想直接同大家講。<br />\n我朋友幫我管理思古井既facebook ac 無緣無故嘅情況之下被ban。<br />\n因此之前嗰個專頁已經無辦法做任何資料發報,<br />\n所以我哋依家臨時臨急嘅情況之下, 將原本facebook page 嘅內容搬字過紙去咗一個新嘅facebook page 。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n希望大家可以幫手多多宣傳,多d去睇入面嘅影片,遲啲仲會有新片更新。其實成件事真係好詭異,究竟係咪d 耶撚係背後整古做怪, 搞到我地連原本嘅facebook page 都用唔到, 而且仲要係今日下午5:30 左右就無啦啦用唔到, 其實我真係心都寒埋, 究竟佢地有幾大嘅影響力先至可以連網絡世界嘅我都封殺埋。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/%E6%80%9D%E5%8F%A4%E4%BA%95%E4%BA%8B%E4%BB%B6%E9%97%9C%E6%B3%A82-1865097490399743/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F%25E6%2580%259D%25E5%258F%25A4%25E4%25BA%2595%25E4%25BA%258B%25E4%25BB%25B6%25E9%2597%259C%25E6%25B3%25A82-1865097490399743%2F&d=nSJvRvahoV7vX7tkwZxFzttKgwQIhJBw7VlnLihElrQ%3D&h=8ed2a2f6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/%E6%80%9D%E5%8F%A4%E4%BA%95%E4%BA%8B%E4%BB%B6%E9%97%9C%E6%B3%A82-1865097490399743/</a>"},{"pid":"25683a8ccaee05efb44b7e7e214134d88bba8dc3","tid":145680,"uid":20943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T12:25:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"26fd6bd106e3f8645a126652780a4f894f47fc3a","tid":145680,"uid":17232,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T12:25:47.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">耶撚死全家</span><span style=\"color: red;\"></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1a5c084c777f6f9ae003535e08462f0784f4a26e","tid":145680